*:[[Rhymes:English:-æp|Rhymes: -æp]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb|wrap|p|ing}}

# {{transitive}} To [[enclose]] (an object) completely in any flexible, thin material such as [[fabric]] or [[paper]].
# {{transitive}} To enclose or coil around an object or organism, as a form of grasping. A prequisite to constriction in snakes.

====Synonyms====
*(''enclose in fabric, paper, etc''): [[enfold]]

====Antonyms====
*[[unwrap]]

